	Crap because 33154 is a patch of just a test.

-optimize='-g';
+optimize='-O2';

-archname='i686-linux-64int';
+archname='i686-linux';

	Let's remove 33154. Next iteration ends here:

----Program----
eval q{use Data::Serializer 0.44};
print $@ ? "N/A" : "OK";
print "\n";

