	@INC expansion. Before I installed Acme::Meta I had this @INC:

cpan[1]> dump @INC
CPAN: Storable loaded ok (v2.15)
Going to read /home/k/.cpan/Metadata
  Database was generated on Thu, 08 Mar 2007 14:08:52 GMT
